Description:
Barozzi Group, fondata nel 1904, è tuttora una società con governance familiare, giunta oggi alla 5° generazione, che comprende tre divisioni di prodotti: 
- Nanotech inside  www.nanotechinside.com vernici termoriflettenti per il risparmio energetico;
- Agrichem by Barozzi, mastici, paraffine e nastri per il vivaismo viticolo e frutticolo; 
- Barozzi Vernici, prodotti vernicianti tradizionali www.barozzivernici.it.

Barozzi Group has been established in 1904 and it still is a family run business. Nowadays, it reached its fifth generation governance and it consists of three divisions: 

- Nanotech inside  https://www.nanotechinside.com/en/ highly energy-efficient, heat-reflecting paints;
- Agrichem by Barozzi, https://www.agrichem.it/en/ tapes, mastics and waxes for fruit tree and vine nursery;
- Barozzi Vernici, https://www.barozzivernici.it/eng/ traditional paints and coatings for buildings.

STRONG3000 has been operating in Egypt for a long time, building strong connections and providing innovative powder coating and enamel coating technologies to the region.

With our new local team, we are further strengthening our presence in Egypt, offering faster support, stronger cooperation, and advanced solutions tailored to the needs of our partners.

Our trusted representatives in Egypt:
 CAPITAL For Chemical Engineering Company
@Ahmed Hamdy
@Waleed Negem
@Ahmed Samir Ghoraba

With their determination, energy, and expertise, STRONG3000 Egypt is ready to take international cooperation to a higher level.

